                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-12-off55 t18020113-12-cd56"></join>, two bushels of oats, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18020113-12-victim158" type="victimName">
                  James 
